"    Algorithm for hypotensive shock and dengue fever",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 621px; height: 672px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Isotonic crystalloid solutions include normal saline (0.9 percent ) and Ringer's lactate. 5 percent albumin is the most commonly used colloid solution.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
